00:03:06.520 --> 00:03:10.630
So they're a series of children's
game books, and the story is written

00:03:10.630 --> 00:03:12.800
from a second-person point of view.

00:03:12.800 --> 00:03:18.160
So the reader assumes a protagonist
role, and they make the choices.

00:03:18.160 --> 00:03:20.468
So they determine the
main character's action,

00:03:20.469 --> 00:03:24.140
the plot's outcome,
