00:31:12.840 --> 00:31:16.220
And there's a purpose to
why it has some movement.

00:31:16.220 --> 00:31:20.430
I think the big problem right now
with prefers-reduced-motion is

00:31:20.430 --> 00:31:22.040
that it's all or nothing, right?

00:31:22.040 --> 00:31:25.230
