for this concept

00:31:25.230 --> 00:31:29.850
of prefers-reduced-motion should
probably be no motion at all,

00:31:29.850 --> 00:31:32.580
because you don't know how much
motion is going to cause someone

00:31:32.580 --> 00:31:37.280
to have a seizure or a migraine
or get nauseous, right?

00:31:37.280 --> 00:31:40.670
You don't want to elicit any
kind of physical reaction

00:31:40.670 --> 00:31:43.320
from your people and the audience.

00:31:43.320 --> 00:31:45.819
So prefers-reduced-motion, reduce,

00:31:45.820 --> 00:31:48.760
that's what I would
suggest right now,

00:31:49.780 --> 00:31:53.300
but once we get the idea... And this
one's almost like fully supported,

00:31:53.300 --> 00:31:55.380
92.59%.

00:31:55.380 --> 00:31:57.460
So pretty robust.

00:31:57.460 --> 00:32:02.530
